Class TemporalQueryRedirector

java.lang.Object
  persistence.TemporalQueryRedirector
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, org.eclipse.persistence.queries.QueryRedirector
public class TemporalQueryRedirector
extends java.lang.Object
implements org.eclipse.persistence.queries.QueryRedirector

This QueryRedirector intercepts read queries on the current types and if there is an effective time property (TemporalHelper.PROPERTY) set on the persistence context then the query is executed against the edition descriptor.

EclipseLink 2.3.1
